episodes.title: Season 14 Queen Ruveal
episodes.plot: Meet all of the new queens competing for the crown on RuPaul's Drag Race Season 14 with reigning champion, Symone.

episodes.title: Big Opening No. 1
episodes.plot: Lizzo guest judges part one of the Season 14 premiere, and a new set of queens stars in a dizzying photo shoot, performs in a talent show and walks the runway in Signature Showstopping Drag.

episodes.title: Big Opening No. 2
episodes.plot: The remaining queens of the brand new cast bring their gifts to a talent show. Singer/songwriter Alicia Keys guest judges.

episodes.title: A Pair of Balls
episodes.plot: The queens put their design skills to the test in a Double Ball challenge, stomping the runway in 42 fashion looks. Christine Chiu guest judges.

episodes.title: She's a Super Tease
episodes.plot: In their first acting challenge, the queens must create iconic moments for a Drag Race Supertease extended trailer. Comedian and host Loni Love (Soul Plane) guest judges.

episodes.title: Save a Queen
episodes.plot: The queens must make parody PSAs for a new charity supporting first-eliminated Drag Race queens; with queens Tempest DuJour, Jaymes Mansfield and Kahmora Hall; pop star Ava Max guest judges.

episodes.title: Glamazon Prime
episodes.plot: Michelle Visage's online shopping has gotten out of hand; in this design challenge, the queens are tasked with making outfits from all the junk she has ordered; Taraji P. Henson (Empire) guest judges.

episodes.title: The Daytona Wind
episodes.plot: The queens don shoulder pads and flex their acting muscles in a campy '80s soap opera; LGBT activist TS Madison guest Judges.

episodes.title: 60s Girl Groups
episodes.plot: The queens read each other for filth, write and perform 60s girl group-inspired songs and pour their hearts into their runway lewks, and comedian Alec Mapa sits in with the judges.

episodes.title: Menzeses
episodes.plot: The queens must lead Drag Con panel discussions about the multi-faceted world of menz: dating, fatherhood, and toxic masculinity; comedian Nicole Byer guest judges.

episodes.title: Snatch Game
episodes.plot: The queens impersonate celebrities in Snatch Game; Drag Race royalty Raven and actress Dove Cameron ("Descendants") play the game.

episodes.title: An Extra Special Episode
episodes.plot: On tonight's extra special episode of Drag Race, RuPaul introduces a twist that leaves the dolls gagging.

episodes.title: Moulin Ru: The Rusical
episodes.plot: The queens go to Gay Paree, in the romantic musical, Moulin Ru; singer Andra Day ("The United States vs. Billie Holiday") guest judges; actor Leslie Jordan ("Will and Grace") guest stars.

episodes.title: The Ross Mathews Roast
episodes.plot: Anastasia Beverly Hills President Norvina stops by as the queens paint the faces of RuPaul and Dolly Parton on a mural, Ross Mathews gets roasted, and Dulcé Sloan sits in with the judges.

episodes.title: Catwalk
episodes.plot: For their final challenge, the Top Five queens design costumes, learn choreography and write song lyrics for their music video debuts in RuPaul's "Catwalk."

episodes.title: Reunited
episodes.plot: The Queens of Season 14 reunite to talk about what happened during the season.

episodes.title: Grand Finale
episodes.plot: The final 5 must face off in a lip sync smackdown for $150,000 and the title of America's Next Drag Superstar.
